Discount Codes:

Planet Botanicals free full sized 3 oz. tin of Shea Butter Balm AND free shipping with purchase of $50 or more code: PBECO730

Salubritas 20% off code: EcoEmi2

*note: you do not have to be a member of Eco Emi to use these discount codes!


-Subscribe to my vlog channel!: http://www.youtube.com/user/sophisticait16

-Tweet Me!: http://www.twitter.com/glamourista16

-Dailybooth: http://www.dailybooth.com/glamourista16

-Join Eco Emi!: http://www.ecoemi.com/join/

I highly recommend this service if you are someone who likes to try out products before committing to buying the full size (even though you do get some full sized products!), are eco friendly, or just want a fun package of goodies every month sent to your door! :D


Disclaimer: I do receive the Eco Emi packages without charge, but honestly my opinions and thoughts of the individual products & service itself are not altered by that. If I don't get a good first impression, I will mention it. If I get a great first impression, I will let you know as well. If I had heard about them earlier, I would have signed up in a heart beat! I truly 100% believe in the service and completely recommend it !
